Changed Deck to be new class type (meaning it now inherits from object) to fix a super() call from a child class Fixed a GinDeck.deal_a_card() Added GinHand.get_card_at_index() Began implementation of GinMatch Added DrawException and StrategyExecutionException GinPlayer now has an action member to handle the advice provided from GinStrategy Implemented GinPlayer.draw(), consult_strategy(), pickup_discard() Began implementing GinPlayer.execute_strategy() -- 3/5 cases done We now hold discarded cards in GinTable's discard_pile Created a parameter-driven MockGinStrategy GinTable now holds the active deck Added many test cases for GinPlayer

Added test_enumerate_all_melds and test_enumerate_all_sets Changed Helper class to be a baseclass so we can inherit its methods and use asserts in them! Added test_deadwood_cards Added test_process_layoff Clarity rename: player_knocked to player_who_knocked Added Helper.compare_arrays_of_cardgroups
Moved card_data into Helper Added stubs for deadwood_cards and process_layoff Changed all usage of helper generators to be called as inherited members
Simplified test_best_action Standardized enumerate_all_melds_and_sets tests to use new inherited Helper methods
